      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "An exceptional A80 Supra Turbo featuring the iconic 2JZ-GTE inline-six with its factory sequential turbocharger configuration fully intact. This specimen boasts the sought-after Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission and a Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring precise power delivery. The mechanical integrity is superlative, exhibiting zero fluid seepage and a chassis that retains its original structural rigidity. The double-wishbone suspension remains compliant, and the four-piston braking system provides firm, linear deceleration. Finished in a concours-level exterior, the interior remains a time-capsule of 90s driver-centric ergonomics, free of any UV degradation or wear. This is a rare, unmodified preservation of Japanese performance engineering.",
