    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional 2019 BMW M3 CS, a vehicle that transcends the standard 'used' label to offer a genuine showroom experience. This masterpiece is finished in a flawless Frozen Dark Grey Metallic, which has been preserved under a professional-grade ceramic coating, ensuring the matte finish remains deep, consistent, and free of any rock chips or swirl marks. The carbon fiber roof, front splitter, and rear diffuser are in perfect structural and cosmetic state. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the Black and Anthracite Alcantara upholstery remains taut, the Merino leather bolsters show zero signs of entry wear, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma. It has been strictly stored in a climate-controlled garage and has never been driven in inclement weather. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule by certified BMW technicians, with a thick folder of records to prove its meticulous upkeep. With incredibly low mileage and a completely stock configuration, this is a turn-key opportunity for the most discerning collector seeking a flawless example of BMW\u2019s engineering peak.",
